A new jewellery house inspired by Kenyan women has launched in Nairobi. Inspired by the Kenyan woman of today, Joo & Co presents a modern yet timeless jewellery collection that is a celebration of grace, beauty and longevity. The Founder and Creative Director Faisal Joo, steeped in family heritage in gemstone trading, merges his passion for sourcing radiant gems across the African continent and craftsmanship in an array of refined designs. Check out some of their ready-to-wear pieces below: